{{vgname|温柔刺客|en=Velvet Assassin|直译为“天鹅绒刺客”}}是一款由[[Replay_Studios|Replay Studios]]開發，由[[Missing_Link_Games|Missing Link Games]]發行的[[隐蔽类游戏|隐蔽类游戏]]。在游戏中，玩家将要扮演一个二战中在纳粹后方作战的英国女间谍——维奥莉特·萨默（Violette Summe）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xbox360fanboy.com/2008/05/13/velvet-assassin-hits-this-fall/|title=Velvet Assassin sneaks onto Xbox 360 this fall|date=2008-05-13|accessdate=2008-05-13|publisher=Xbox 360 Fanboy|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514172536/http://www.xbox360fanboy.com/2008/05/13/velvet-assassin-hits-this-fall/|archivedate=2008-05-14}}</ref>。游戏剧情受到英国军情六处特工[[維歐蕾特·薩博|維歐蕾特·薩博]]传奇般的真实行动经历启发<ref>"''Velvet Assassin'': Suede Stealth," ''Game Informer'' 184 (August 2008): 68.</ref>。

